'''Dawn Creekmore''' (born February 28, 1965) is an American politician who served in the [[Arkansas House of Representatives]] from the 27th district from 2005 to 2011.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.arkleg.state.ar.us/assembly/2009/R/Pages/MemberProfile.aspx?member=D.%20Creekmore |title=Dawn Creekmore |publisher=Arkleg.state.ar.us |date= |accessdate=2018-09-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.arkansasonline.com/news/2009/jul/16/rep-creekmore-announces-bid-state-senate--20090716/?f=trilakes |title=Rep. Creekmore announces bid for state Senate District 22 seat |publisher=Arkansasonline.com |date=2009-07-16 |accessdate=2018-09-24}}</ref>

