The '''Oxfordshire Museums Council''' ('''OMC''') is an organisation representing [[museum]]s in [[Oxfordshire]], [[England]].<ref name="southeastmuseums">{{cite web| url=http://southeastmuseums.org/oxfordshire-museums-council | title=Oxfordshire Museums Council | publisher=South East Museum Development Programme | accessdate=30 July 2017 }}</ref>
OMC was founded in 1983 and represents around 40 museums. It is a [[registered charity]] (no. 296734) that is formed of representatives from museums operated by the [[local authority]] and [[Oxford University]], as well as independent and volunteer museums.<ref name="occ">{{cite web| url=http://mycouncil.oxford.gov.uk/mgOutsideBodyDetails.aspx?ID=295 | title=Oxfordshire Museums Council | publisher=[[Oxford City Council]] | accessdate=30 July 2017 }}</ref>
